name: Quick-sort
body:
# quick-sort
Super Fast Quick Sort

To Run, just use:

  `QuickSortEppinger.ej_quick_sort3(array, 0, array.length)`
  
Results vary, but should be about 4 to 5 times faster than `java.util.Arrays.sort(array)`
